{"tid":594692,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"話時話，娥娥仲係咪處？（內含海量J圖）","createTime":"2018-03-16T04:54:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-16T05:21:29.000Z","uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3dba45d649bf02dccd99d4b6c578dc9aa518a5c7","tid":594692,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T04:54:53.000Z","msg":"作為一個政支時事關心者，我成日都喺到諗我偶像，娥娥，究竟仲係咪處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔得！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 娥娥女神係處依件事係不容置疑㗎！！但係佢咁正咁索，喺政界打滾咁耐，點會無富家子弟，政界巨人去拜於佢石榴群下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果我有啲本錢我都鳩衝左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/16/123744_5bbbcc141a17abbf5d6e49fe289b8c5a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F16%2F123744_5bbbcc141a17abbf5d6e49fe289b8c5a.png&h=42a6a4f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢白滑滑嘅肌膚，望落仲後生過依家嗰啲所謂嘅明星，天然過佢地一百倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/16/123929_402fbca3ae70ba2a27d1f229c7d1cfa0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F16%2F123929_402fbca3ae70ba2a27d1f229c7d1cfa0.png&h=1f8c3cf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當你以為佢依個年紀佢個格甩底一定係一片黑草源，但係估唔到仲乾淨白滑過一個高級酒店嘅馬桶表面<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪好想奶呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/16/123931_5129d994e0b40ad3ff3a491c74afb303.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F16%2F123931_5129d994e0b40ad3ff3a491c74afb303.png&h=5d48466c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n望住佢嘅背影，青春嘅肉體卻帶住一股無奈嘅滄桑感，白滑嘅雙腿為男士帶黎一股澎湃嘅血流衝動<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/16/123956_89f353965ce562ec997d2d0fcf83dd72.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F16%2F123956_89f353965ce562ec997d2d0fcf83dd72.png&h=0f11afaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不止係熟女，更有一股可愛青春無敵感<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 童真中又無邪嘅笑容令各男士都想立刻娶佢為妻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/16/124014_83251724d707a583d6a2d7e365ba175a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F16%2F124014_83251724d707a583d6a2d7e365ba175a.png&h=1330a9a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最重要係佢嘅時尚感，連走古風都不忘露出性感嘅胸部，係咪想為自己唔小心失去議席向公眾露出sek屎八字波道歉呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當我問佢樹枝少年係咪感情台唯一清泉，佢咁答返我。果然係女神，連我依個死毒撚都咁支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 全中國十三億蟲都感動了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/16/123926_ac6bcc1702b56ec6fe7217bc863aa0ba.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F16%2F123926_ac6bcc1702b56ec6fe7217bc863aa0ba.png&h=330af6cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到依家，大家心入面都應該有個答案，甚至從你自己嘅身體反應都得到答案了，但係，我唔會相信，娥娥一定都仲係處黎㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca9b8a2ba24d3c952765fd5d77e02a9dbe65b7f5","tid":594692,"uid":165024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T04:55:37.000Z","msg":"圖片: 機會很少"},{"pid":"ce6d36a451257d49a2c127b9f823f76c88510979","tid":594692,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T04:56:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"64e9d92e4f374bfa7978b66d591ad0b096f33a2c","tid":594692,"uid":23170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T04:57:16.000Z","msg":"連登咁多垃圾方國珊打手，論智慧論美貌點都係娥娥優勝啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab770837beb95313b1af27c3c218ceb9ef16761b","tid":594692,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T05:00:31.000Z","msg":"太瘦差評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72e209f3745b0e8aedd8acc0d56b75f2c58dce54","tid":594692,"uid":40350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T05:03:09.000Z","msg":"過唔到良心 負評"},{"pid":"afdcd38e83280fa74a25f8dd88a09862728206fe","tid":594692,"uid":23170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ab770837beb95313b1af27c3c218ceb9ef16761b","tid":594692,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T05:00:31.000Z","msg":"太瘦差評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T05:08:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/16/130717_e6cfdf3ddf47d67d3eb3c17e5518d3e8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F16%2F130717_e6cfdf3ddf47d67d3eb3c17e5518d3e8.png&h=75db0b0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n瘦底大波唔好咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a45b8b99ebf7563d2749cbc85ec45d9e3099eb9e","tid":594692,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T05:14:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>太瘦差評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/16/130717_e6cfdf3ddf47d67d3eb3c17e5518d3e8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F16%2F130717_e6cfdf3ddf47d67d3eb3c17e5518d3e8.png&h=75db0b0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n瘦底大波唔好咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我愛肥妹仔阿阿阿阿阿阿阿阿阿阿阿阿阿阿"},{"pid":"6f0e382fd9875a39e4f45712541ebb9210656ad3","tid":594692,"uid":175896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T05:21:29.000Z","msg":"好似141咁 圖真J死 一開門就嚇死"}]}